General.Name: Guard Therapeutics International AB
General.Description: Guard Therapeutics International AB (publ), a pharmaceutical company, identifies, develops, and commercializes therapies for the diagnosis and treatment of acute kidney injuries in Sweden. It offers ROSGard, a biological drug candidate that prevents kidney damage by protecting, cleaning, and repairing the exposed cells and tissues. The company was formerly known as A1M Pharma AB (publ) and changed its name to Guard Therapeutics International AB (publ) in October 2019. Guard Therapeutics International AB (publ) was incorporated in 2008 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
